
1.The mtr utility is a network diagnostic tool to troubleshoot the network bottlenecks. It combines the functionality of both ping and traceroute. 
mtr google.com
mtr -n --report google.com


2.Get all DNS records 
dig twiter.com ANY
dig www.google.com A +short

3.List all network interfaces
sudo  tcpdump --list-interfaces
sudo tcpdump -i any

4.List open files
lsof -i :8080

5.List all listening ports
ss -t -r state established
ss -t -r state listening

5.To troubleshoot web server connectivity 
curl http://google.com -I

6.If you want to limit ping 
ping -c 1 google.com
